on Dark Score Lake.

867
01:05:47,905 --> 01:05:49,345
I can't say.

868
01:05:49,345 --> 01:05:52,105
Even in your limited experience,

869
01:05:52,145 --> 01:05:54,385
do you think that most people
obey the speed limit

870
01:05:54,505 --> 01:05:55,625
