[Sighs] Oh, my God, I'm such an idiot.

972
01:10:27,265 --> 01:10:28,625
No, no.
It's not your fault.

973
01:10:28,625 --> 01:10:32,945
It's just... Messy.
Complicated.

974
01:10:32,945 --> 01:10:34,745
Plus the fact...

975
01:10:34,825 --> 01:10:37,325
I keep thinking that Jo...

976
01:10:39,205 --> 01:10:41,265
That she brought me here.

977
01:10:41,343 --> 01:10:42,263
Jo...

978
01:10:42,479 --> 01:10:44,099
brought me here.

979
01:10:44,105 --> 01:10:45,905
After she died, she brought you here?

980
01:10:46,145 --> 01:10:47,145
For a reason.

981
01:10:47,485 --> 01:10:49,165
Like what?

982
01:10:52,505 --> 01:10:55,025
I don't know...
Yet.

983
01:10:56,905 --> 01:10:58,185
Crazy, right?
[Laughs]

984
01:10:58,825 --> 01:10:59,985
Not to me.

985
01:11:00,185 --> 01:11:02,145
Yeah, well,
maybe she did bring me here

986
01:11:02,225 --> 01:11:03,785
so she could finally tell me what...

987
01:11:05,305 --> 01:11:08,225
She was doing here.

988
01:11:09,465 --> 01:11:11,705
Or maybe it's to get you
to write again.

989
01:11:13,025 --> 01:11:13,705
Yeah.

990
01:11:15,305 --> 01:11:16,505
Maybe you're right.

991
01:11:24,265 --> 01:11:24,905
Okay.

992
01:11:30,825 --> 01:11:31,625
[Sighs]

993
01:11:36,425 --> 01:11:37,505
[Sighs]

994
01:11:46,305 --> 01:11:47,105
There you are.

995
01:11:48,105 --> 01:11:48,785
Look at you.

996
01:11:49,825 --> 01:11:51,265
Just look at you.

997
01:11:52,025 --> 01:11:53,025
Hmm.

998
01:12:02,465 --> 01:12:03,305
All right.

999
01:12:04,265 --> 01:12:05,705
Let's just move that there.

1000
01:12:06,505 --> 01:12:07,865
There you go.

1001
01:12:09,105 --> 01:12:10,305
There you go.

1002
01:12:12,545 --> 01:12:13,825
[Sighs]

1003
01:12:38,425 --> 01:12:39,745
"She lit a cigarette

1004
01:12:41,025 --> 01:12:43,105
