1007
01:12:50,065 --> 01:12:52,385
It made me feel like screaming.

1008
01:12:53,345 --> 01:12:55,665
It made me feel like screaming.

1009
01:12:56,345 --> 01:12:59,385
[Laughs]

1010
01:13:05,305 --> 01:13:06,625
Thank you, Jo.

1011
01:13:08,545 --> 01:13:10,705
I always said
I couldn't write without you.

1012
01:13:13,665 --> 01:13:15,225
I just had to find you.

