01:14:07,465 --> 01:14:11,825
Yeah.

1017
01:14:11,825 --> 01:14:13,745
Ah.

1018
01:14:13,825 --> 01:14:15,345
[Sighs]

1019
01:14:20,105 --> 01:14:21,425
29 pages.

1020
01:14:21,465 --> 01:14:23,105
Holy shit.

1021
01:14:24,065 --> 01:14:24,905
God, I'm good.

1022
01:14:25,985 --> 01:14:27,425
Oh, yeah.

1023
01:14:30,345 --> 01:14:31,105
