1614
02:00:50,020 --> 02:00:51,660
Sorry to hear that.

1615
02:00:52,940 --> 02:00:54,140
What did you two talk about?

1616
02:00:54,540 --> 02:00:57,020
Oh, nothing much.

1617
02:00:57,780 --> 02:00:59,980
She had a bunch of questions
about the history

1618
02:01:00,020 --> 02:01:01,220
of Dark Score Lake.

