1660
02:03:21,260 --> 02:03:26,060
We were all heat up from the show.

1661
02:03:26,100 --> 02:03:28,100
¶ A small port wine

1662
02:03:28,180 --> 02:03:32,100
and it was Max who suggested
we pay Sara a visit afterwards.

1663
02:03:35,900 --> 02:03:40,140
Of course, none of us knew
what Max had planned.

1664
02:03:40,180 --> 02:03:43,220
At least that's what
I've been telling myself

1665
02:03:43,220 --> 02:03:45,300
all these years.

1666
02:03:45,300 --> 02:03:47,420
I liked your show.

1667
02:03:47,460 --> 02:03:49,340
[Chuckles]

1668
02:03:49,380 --> 02:03:52,940
Well, thank you, sugar.

1669
02:03:52,980 --> 02:03:54,740
Maybe I'll see you at the next one.

1670
02:03:54,780 --> 02:03:56,500
