1671
02:03:56,540 --> 02:03:57,740
Don't you turn away from me.

1672
02:03:57,780 --> 02:03:58,620
[Grunts]

1673
02:03:59,180 --> 02:04:01,460
Liking my singing
doesn't buy you a right to me.

1674
02:04:03,300 --> 02:04:04,420
Stop her!

1675
02:04:12,300 --> 02:04:15,140
You think you can sing the way you do

1676
02:04:15,180 --> 02:04:16,580
and get away with it, huh?

1677
02:04:16,620 --> 02:04:19,060
You think you and your
kind can boil our blood

1678
02:04:19,100 --> 02:04:21,940
and not give us what we want
when you're done, huh?

1679
02:04:21,980 --> 02:04:25,700
Come here.

1680
