[Fabric ripping]

1684
02:04:38,380 --> 02:04:40,180
You going to tell me
you're sorry, bitch?

1685
02:04:40,220 --> 02:04:42,300
You going to beg me for forgiveness?

1686
02:04:42,340 --> 02:04:43,900
[Laughing] I don't beg for nothing...

1687
02:04:43,980 --> 02:04:45,500
[Grunting]

1688
02:04:45,540 --> 02:04:48,100
Especially not for no little boy.

1689
02:04:50,820 --> 02:04:53,220
[Yelps, laughs]

1690
02:04:58,140 --> 02:05:00,020
Go home, honey!

1691
02:05:00,060 --> 02:05:02,220
Now! Run!

1692
02:05:02,700 --> 02:05:03,620
Mommy!

1693
02:05:03,780 --> 02:05:06,780
Run, Kisha baby, run!
Run!

1694
02:05:06,780 --> 02:05:07,980
Where's all your tough talk now?

1695
02:05:08,060 --> 02:05:09,340
