1840
02:14:26,720 --> 02:14:29,320
If they or any of their
descendants had daughters...

1841
02:14:31,200 --> 02:14:34,720
They would do the same horrible
things to their little girls

1842
02:14:35,160 --> 02:14:37,320
that they had done to Sara Tidwell

1843
02:14:37,400 --> 02:14:39,160
and her little girl.

1844
02:14:39,160 --> 02:14:42,560
Their descendants included
Buddy Jellison

1845
02:14:42,640 --> 02:14:44,960
and Bill Dean's fathers.

1846
02:14:44,960 --> 02:14:47,880
[Thunder booms]

1847
02:14:47,920 --> 02:14:50,040
That explains why they drowned
their daughters

1848
02:14:50,080 --> 02:14:52,120
all those years later.

1849
02:14:52,120 --> 02:14:55,880
One of that group was
my grandfather, Harold Noonan...

1850
02:14:55,960 --> 02:14:58,560
No!
Please.

1851
02:14:58,600 --> 02:15:02,160
Who willed the lake house
to Jo and myself.

1852
02:15:03,760 --> 02:15:06,320
Did your father murder your sister?

1853
02:15:06,360 --> 02:15:08,080
- No, no, no,
I-I didn't have any sisters.

1854
02:15:08,080 --> 02:15:10,320
There was just Sid and me.

1855
02:15:15,680 --> 02:15:18,400
Oh, my God, Mike, don't you see?

1856
02:15:18,480 --> 02:15:20,280
This is the final piece of the puzzle.

1857
02:15:20,360 --> 02:15:22,960
This is why Jo didn't want
to tell you she was pregnant.

1858
02:15:23,720 --> 02:15:25,400
Jo had learned of the curse.

1859
02:15:25,400 --> 02:15:27,080
That's why she had all
those library books.

1860
02:15:27,120 --> 02:15:30,520
That's why she had Sara Tidwell's
albums and... and photographs.

1861
02:15:31,120 --> 02:15:33,680
It's why she went to see
that man in the rest home.

1862
02:15:34,160 --> 02:15:35,920
That's why she used to visit Dark Score

1863
02:15:35,920 --> 02:15:37,640
lake all those weekends
before she died.

1864
02:15:37,720 --> 02:15:39,320
She wasn't having an affair.

1865
02:15:40,120 --> 02:15:42,000
